'''Secrets''' in Dragon Warrior include hidden features, optimal strategies, and game knowledge.

== Secret Items ==

=== Erdrick's Token ===
Hidden in a swamp tile south of Cantlin.

'''How to Find:'''
* Walk to the swamp south of Cantlin
* Search while standing on the swamp
* Required for Erdrick's Armor

=== Erdrick's Armor ===
The best armor in the game, found in Hauksness.

'''Location:'''
* In the ruins of Hauksness
* Search specific tile in the ruined city
* Must have Erdrick's Token to confirm identity

=== Fairy Flute ===
Used to put the Golem to sleep.

'''Location:'''
* Obtained from NPC in Kol
* Required to safely pass Cantlin

== Hidden Mechanics ==

=== Running from Battle ===
The success rate for running depends on:
* Your level vs enemy level
* Agility stat
* Random factor

=== Critical Hits ===
Critical hits deal damage ignoring enemy defense:
* Base rate depends on equipment
* Dragon Bane has higher critical rate vs dragons

=== Sleep Spell Mechanics ===
Sleep has varying success rates based on enemy resistance:
* Very effective on many bosses
* Some enemies are immune

== Passwords ==

The game uses a password (Spell of Restoration) system:

'''Password Contains:'''
* Hero name
* Current experience points
* Gold amount
* Inventory items
* Quest progress

'''Tips:'''
* Write passwords carefully
* Case and spacing matter
* Invalid passwords reset progress

