== Tips ==

'''Combat:'''
* HEAL spell is essential early
* SLEEP works on many enemies
* HURT/HURTMORE for groups not needed (single enemies only in DW1)

'''Gold Farming:'''
* Goldmen near Hauksness drop good gold
* Metal Slimes give high experience but flee

'''Experience:'''
* Grind levels before major fights
* Return to castle to heal rather than using herbs
* Inn costs scale with level

== Easter Eggs ==

=== Princess Gwaelin ===
After rescuing her, she asks if you love her:
* Saying "No" results in repeated asking
* Eventually must say "Yes" to progress
* Carrying her through dungeons has dialogue

=== King Lorik ===
Various dialogue changes based on progress:
* Comments on equipment
* Acknowledges major achievements
* Different endings based on actions

